        "translations": {
          "en": "Muhammad b. Musa b. al-Mutawakkil (may Allah have mercy on him) narrated to us. He said: Muhammad b. Abi Abdullah al-Kufi narrated to us from Ishaq b. Muhammad, from Hamza b. Muhammad. He said:",
